			<td>Estatística e Delineamento <svg class="bi bi-chevron-down" fill="currentColor" height="16" viewbox="0 0 16 16" width="16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"> <path d="M1.646 4.646a.5.5 0 0 1 .708 0L8 10.293l5.646-5.647a.5.5 0 0 1 .708.708l-6 6a.5.5 0 0 1-.708 0l-6-6a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.708" fill-rule="evenodd"></path> </svg></td>
